         The Governor's Reading Professional Development Institutes

                                  presents

                  A One-Day, Follow-Up Reading Workshop for
             LAUSD K-5 Elementary Administrators in grades K-5.
               The agenda will address the full implementation
       of Open Court 2000 with emphasis on observation and monitoring.

   All administrators who attended one of the Governor's Reading
   Professional Development Institutes May 2001 through October 2001 are
   invited to register.

   On-line registration is now CLOSED. You may still attend by registering
   on-site. Use the following information as your guide.

   DATES

   Wednesday, November 28, 2001

   OR Thursday, November 29, 2001

   OR Friday, November 30, 2001

   LOCATION

   Wilshire Grand Hotel

   930 Wilshire Blvd.

   Los Angeles, CA 90017

   213-688-7777

   SCHEDULE

   7:00 a.m. - 8:00 a.m. Registration and Continental Breakfast

   8:00 a.m. - 12:00 p.m. Morning Session

   12:00 p.m. - 1:00 p.m. Lunch (provided)

   1:00 p.m. - 3:00 p.m. Afternoon Session

   PARKING

   Validated parking is available in the underground Wilshire Grand
   Parking Garage at the corner of 7th and Francisco Streets, or at the
   Ernst & Young Garage on Francisco St.

   REGISTRATION

   Registration will be located on the banquet level. At that time you
   will receive your conference materials. A continental breakfast will be
   served in conjunction with registration.
